<a href="#0" id="0">For the first task, the binary identification task, the metaphoricity of a sentence was computed by taking the percentage of participants who identified it as metaphoric.</a>
<a href="#1" id="1">The metaphoricity values for this experiment were calculated in the same way the percentage of participants who rated a sentence as highly metaphoric.</a>
<a href="#2" id="2">The participants were asked to order the sentences from the least metaphoric to the most metaphoric.</a>
<a href="#3" id="3">The metaphoricity value was computed by taking the percentage of participants who identified a sentence as the most metaphoric of the three given sentences.</a>
<a href="#4" id="4">Thus, for the number x of metaphors in the genre, the x sentences with the top metaphoricity values were identified as metaphoric.</a>
